    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad tee ne klausija / bet apzeettinajahs pahrgalwigi / pehz fawu Tehwu Pahrgalwibas/ kas eekſch to KUNGU fawu Deewu ne bij tizzejscht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta mizzinaja tee winna Baufkus/ un winna Derribu/ ko tas ar winnu Tehweem bij darrijs/ un winna Leezibas/ ko tas winnu Starpâ bij apleezinajs/ un dsinnahs us Neleetibu / un ktua neleeschi/ un gahje teem Pa-ganeem pakat/ kas apkahrt teem bija/ no ka tas KUNGS teem bij pawehlejs/ ka teem ne bij ta Darriht ka winni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tee atstahjebs no wiſch feem Banfleen tu KUNGA fa- wa Deewa / un darrija few is-leetas Bildeg/ diwi Tektus / un darrija arridsan Elka Meschns / un paklannitjahs preekſch wiﬀu Debbes Spehku / un kalpoja Baalam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee likke arridsan fawus Deblus un fawas Meitas zaar Ugguni eet/ un dewahs us Sih-letchanahn/ un eezeentja Putnu-Brehfschann / un pahrdewahs kann darriht preekſch ta KUN-GA Azzim / ka tee winnu apkaitinaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz apskaitahs tas KUNGS tohti pahr Israëlu/ ka wiſch tohs no few atmette/ ka ne neeka atlifte/ ka ta Zilts Juh da ween.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "(Ir Juhda ne turreja ta KUNGA fawa Deewa Bauf-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "lus/ bet tee staigaja Israëta L tumds/ ko tee bij darrijſchi.)\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atmette tas KUN wisfu Israëka Dsimnumu / u apbehdinaja tohs/ un dewe tom term Laupitajeem Rohkâ / mehr wiſch tohs no jew bij amettis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo wiſch noſchkihre fraelu no Dahvida Namma/ i tee darrija Jerobeamu Neeba Dehlu par Fehniku/ un Jerob ains nowehrse Israëlu no KUNGA/ un darrija tohs leeleem Grehkeeni grehkoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta staigaja tee Israë Behrni eekſch wiﬀeem Jerobe ma Grehkeem/ ko tas bij darrija tee ne atstahjebs no teem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Teekans tas KUNG Israëlu no jewis atmette/ itt ta tas bij runnajs/ zaur wiſchee faweem Kalpeem teem Praue scheem. Ta tappe Israels no was Semmes aiswests us Apriju/ lihds schodeen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Fehninsch no Arijas atiwedde (Landis) no Bebeles/un no Kutas/un no Ava un no Eemata/ un no Sewa wain / un likke tohs dsihw eekſch Samarijas Pilssahteenu to Israëta Behrnu Weeta/ tee cemantoja Samartju / dsihwoja eekſch tahs pasch Pilstahteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tee nu tur fahzedsi woht/ un to KUNGU ne bihj ahs/ tad fuhtija tas KUNG\n"
    }
  ],
